channel.description:
* MOVE IF NECESSARY. *
I simply need some guidance on how to deobfuscate a client with a 317 revision and base of Delta. If you would like to make it simpler and contact me on Skype, just PM me and I will send you my information.
Thank you,
~ TF4LY ~

item.title: Help
item.dc:creator: @pure2ownage Pure_
item.description:
@pure2ownage wrote:

So you’re the person who sk8r asked me for. This will not be easy and if it was obfuscated in a way other than the official rs-client which (which I suspect) then you’re in for a long hard day. I would recommend comparing function structure with a deob client or going off some form of file structure as a whole.

You can also check my repo and see how my commits change the client as I deob the official rs client.
[/quote]
